消费者取消了机票的预订，尤其是对济州航空等廉价航空公司预订机票的取消大幅增加。 韩国旅游业界普遍认为，此次济州航空客机失事事件将对旅游业产生巨大打击。12 月初，尹锡悦总统宣布紧急戒严后导致政局不稳定，韩元大幅贬值，致使消费心理萎缩，已经给旅游业造成严重影响，而这一次济州航空失事事件更是给韩国旅游业界带来「致命一击」。 当地时间 12 月 29 日，一架韩国济州航空的客机在位于韩国全罗南道的务安机场着陆时，偏离跑道后撞上机场围墙。除 2 人获救外，机上其余 179 人全部遇难，这是在韩国国内发生的伤亡最严重的空难事故。客机失事事故致游客大批取消旅游计划，韩国旅游业受重创 | 界面新闻 · 快讯"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-4c916a8045dbfa1fb0faaa57d716c284_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "5 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/8251182483"}}, "attached_info": "CkEIuIKKz6/XqYMYEAMaCTExMjYyNjU3MiDD1Mi7BjAAONwDQAtyCjgyNTExODI0ODN4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "12_1735719229.795827", "card_id": "Q_8415042525", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 69}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价《黑神话：悟空》获得 2024 年 Steam 大奖年度最佳游戏等三项奖项?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "另外两项奖项分别为：纵使手残仍大爱奖、杰出剧情游戏奖。 Steam 大奖 - 2024"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-4d73d74b3ede72cd28728fe82ae4102d_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "4.9 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/8415042525"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIuIKKz6/XqYMYEAMaCTExMjY1OTMzMyCctdK7BjAAOHJADHIKODQxNTA0MjUyNXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "13_1735719229.796177", "card_id": "Q_513065666", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 703}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "梦，标准读音是 mèng，为什么很多歌手唱出来的是 mòng？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https:/